- [ ] Save Preferences persists to localStorage and shows a confirmation message; data shape is validated with Array.isArray checks.
- [ ] Revoke Consent clears persisted data and resets toggles to defaults; all runtime safety guards are in place.
- [ ] No runtime errors due to null/undefined results; all array operations guarded with (items ?? []) or Array.isArray checks.

